name: Atticus Kongstrong #678
description: The older of the two kong twins by 13.37 seconds. At the age of 3, Atticus Kong was able to broker a peace deal between India and Pakistan. At the age of 7, both he and his brother Benedict simultaneously scored 1700 on the SAT, a score previously thought impossible. It is theorized that the brothers travelled back in time in order to add questions to the test in order to achieve this score. A master of Engineering and Physics, Atticus was able to create a device that can power the homes of every person on the planet for a year using a single banana peel. Atticus likes long walks on the beach and despite being the most eligible bachelor in his country, has decided to devote his time to his work, only going on occasional dates when he's not working on a new invention or groundbreaking scientific paper.
